   <!-- Start Content Area --> 
   <div id="main"> 
    <p><img class="border" alt="" width="484" height="202" src="/Images/Mail cropped.jpg"></p> 
    <h4 style="text-align: justify">We are here to meet your mailing needs, help cut your postage expenses and speed the delivery of your mail. Our commitment is to meet your expectations by providing the highest level of customer service possible.</h4> 
    <div class="column23" style="height: 197px; width: 282px"> 
     <h6 style="text-align: left"><em><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51)">We offer a wide range of services to meet your needs. Bulk Mail, Inter-Campus, Incoming and Outgoing mail, Scotmail and Messenger Services, as well as addressing mail, and a bulletin page that&nbsp;is updated regularly with important mailing news. Mail Services provides most services offered by the United States Postal Service including certified, registered, express and insured mail.</span></em>&nbsp;</h6> 
     <p>&nbsp;</p> 
     <p>&nbsp;</p> 
    </div> 
    <p>&nbsp;</p> 
    <p>&nbsp;</p> 
    <p>&nbsp;<a onclick="window.open(this.href,'TierRates','resizable=yes,location=no,menubar=no,scrollbars=yes,status=no,toolbar=no,fullscreen=no,dependent=no,status'); return false" href="/Mail_Rates/14MS-Tier Rates-FY1415-Approved.pdf"><img alt="" width="107" height="97" src="/Images/Tier Rates Env copy.jpg"></a></p> 
    <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> 
    <p>&nbsp;</p> 
    <div class="boxB">
     Mail Services Customer Services Representatives are ready to assist you with all of your mailing needs. Please call or e-mail us whenever the need arises. You will find our telephone numbers and e-mail addresses under "
     <a href="/contact_us.html">contact us</a>". Our service representatives will monitor the progress of your mailing request as they are processed from setup to&nbsp;completion. For the best results in mailing, contact our services representatives when you begin planning your project.
     <br> We are here to meet your mailing needs, help cut your postage expenses and speed the delivery of your mail. Our commitment is to meet your expectations by providing the highest quality product and level of customer service possible.&nbsp;
    </div> 
    <p><img class="img_L_borderless" alt="" style="height: 99px; width: 92px" src="/Images/Envelope3.png"></p> 
    <p>&nbsp;</p> 
    <div class="boxC"> 
     <h4 style="margin-left: 120px"><span style="font-size: small">Vision<strong><br> </strong></span></h4> 
     <p style="margin-left: 120px"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51)"><span><span>To provide mailing and&nbsp;shipping services to the University of California Riverside at a maximum level of efficiency and accountability, and to meet the needs and expectations of our customers.</span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(128,128,128)"><span style="font-size: small"><br> </span></span></p> 
     <p style="margin-left: 120px"><span style="color: rgb(128,128,128)"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51)"><span>Thank you&nbsp;for your support.<br> John R. Salazar, Manager</span></span></span></span></p> 
     <p style="margin-left: 120px"><a target="_blank" href="http://campusmap.ucr.edu/campusMap.php?loc=CORP"><span style="font-size: small">Click here for a map to our office</span></a></p> 
     <p style="margin-left: 120px">(<em><span style="font-family: Arial">Mail Services is located in the Corporation Yard adjacent to the Material Management / Receiving dock</span></em><span style="font-family: Arial">).</span></p> 
    </div> 
    <p>&nbsp;</p> 
   </div> 
